  "title": "Café Service Crew",
  "description": "<p><strong></strong></p><p><strong>Locations:</strong> Waterway Point, PLQ, 100AM, Ngee Ann City, Great World, VivoCity, Orchard</p><ul><li><p>Greet every guest like a friend. Your energy sets the tone.</p></li><li><p>Become a menu expert. Help guests discover their new favorite drink or bite.</p></li><li><p>Take orders with care and deliver service that’s both prompt and personal.</p></li><li><p>Keep the café sparkling, stocked, and inviting for everyone.</p></li><li><p>Work smoothly with your crew and kitchen team to keep the vibe positive and operations flawless.</p></li><li><p>Assist with daily opening, closing, and restocking routines with pride.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p><strong>Salary:</strong> $2,300 – $2,800 per month.</p></li><li><p><strong>Work-Life Balance:</strong> A stable 40-hour work week with 2 scheduled rest days.</p></li><li><p><strong>Benefits:</strong> Annual bonus (AWS), medical & dental insurance, and 12 days of paid annual leave (which grows over time!).</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>EA Personnel R22110043 Tan Eng Kang</p><p>EA License 21C0430 A Dreamworks Company Pte Ltd</p>",
